<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Establishment Subscription - PHLOII</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="checkout-container">
        <div class="checkout-content">
            <h2 class="checkout-heading">Join PHLOII - Premium Establishment Listing</h2>
            <p class="description">PHLOII offers a platform for exclusive establishments to showcase their properties to a wider audience. Unlock premium visibility and features by subscribing today.</p>
            
            <div class="price-info">
                <p class="price-text"><span class="price">$99/month</span></p>
            </div>

            <div class="subscription-info">
                <p class="info-text">
                    This subscription allows your establishment to be featured prominently on PHLOII, giving you access to our broad customer base and enhancing your business presence.
                </p>
            </div>

            <form action="/api/v1/hotel/checkout" method="POST" class="checkout-form">
                <input type="hidden" name="hotelId" value="<%= hotelId %>">
                <button type="submit" class="checkout-button">Proceed to Checkout</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
